      "note": "digest",
      "abstract": "AN ACT relating to the protection of constitutional rights; prohibiting the disclosure or use of information relating to firearms and ammunition sales as specified; providing requirements for disclosure of information relating to firearms and ammunition sales; requiring investigations as specified; authorizing civil actions as specified; authorizing criminal and civil penalties; providing and amending definitions; and providing for an effective date."
    }
  ],
